title: PIANO MASTERCLASS - Oscar Peterson Demonstrates Jazz Piano Styles! Piano Tutorial Remastered
description:
PIANO MASTERCLASS - Oscar Peterson Demonstrates Jazz Piano Styles! Piano Tutorial Remastered.  https://youtu.be/QqPhypQAhU8 This is an edited interview with Oscar Peterson. I have remastered the video and audio of the old footage, so you can hear Oscar's wisdom and piano playing in high quality stereo sound. Oscar demonstrates various Jazz piano styles, and the video closes with Oscar playing an improvisation which demonstrates his own style and playing. 
These videos are for educational purposes only, and no copyright violations have been intended. These exercise videos and the edited and remastered piano Masterclass are copyright 2019 by Terry Dean founder of Piano Tutorials on youtube.

You might also like my unique collection of Oscar Peterson's piano exercises. Here's the playlist. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QqPhypQAhU8&list=PLHcAKuB15S91xHuH5RsgxnGTYfxKCtyJx

I hope you enjoy this great collection of exercises and footage of Oscar Peterson. Please leave your comments and questions in the comments section. And it would be great if you were to subscribe to my channel because it helps me know that you like and enjoy my videos, and also brings us together as part of a nice piano tutorial community online. 
Thanks for watching, reading and listening. Have fun! Terry Dean :)
